A son has been arrested for the murder of his 55-year-old traditional healer father.According to Dube police spokesperson the incident happened on Tuesday around 4.30pm.It alleged that when the incident happened the younger sister and mother were outside while they heard a gunshot from the house where the father and son were listening to music.&#8220;After a gunshot was heard the suspect stopped the sister and mother from entering the house, police said. The neighbours called the police and when they arrived the son opened the house.There the son pointed to the gun inside the kitchen unit.The father s body, decapitated and with his private parts hacked off, was found by police in his traditional surgery.Police said the body had been mutilated using a hacksaw and knife.The private parts were inside the bag and head inside a refrigerator in the dining room.A murder case was opened and the son arrested.-TNA Reporter